data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, BUYER CHANGED AREA THEY WANTED TO BE IN! Awesome potential in this 3 bedroom, 2 full bath desirable RANCH home in Leaf River! If you need space, this is the place for you! Kitchen has an eat in area, nice cabinets and plenty of room to work. You will love the convenient 1st floor laundry area right off the kitchen to save you steps! Formal dining area right next to the kitchen has tons of light and perfect for family get togethers. The partially finished lower level has a 2nd kitchen, bar area and a lot of room to entertain and relax! Not only do you get the storage/living space this beautiful home w/attached 2 car garage offers, but you get an ADDITIONAL LOT next door with a detached 3 car garage! Boats, trailers, snowmobiles.. no problem! The backyard offers a handy covered picnic shelter with electricity! City water and sewer, vinyl siding, central air and electric heating. Appliances will stay. This home needs some updating such as flooring and vanities but the layout is wonderful and ready to make your own! Schedule a showing soon before this great property is taken!
